==Appearance in media==
A modified Bentley Continental GT appeared in Season 4, Episode 2 (A Massive Hunt) of the Amazon Prime Video original series The Grand Tour, and later a cameo reappearance in Clarkson&#x27;s Farm. It was driven by Jeremy Clarkson, and was modified car with long-travel shock absorbers, armor-plated steel running on the belly of the car from the front to the back, big chunky tyres, a snorkel, off-road lights, and also repainted the car from blue to green. The car is currently on display at the Bentley headquarters.

